1. *Snimanje* je počelo u 8 ujutru. (Recording began at 8 am.)
2. Potrebno je napraviti *snimanje* zvuka za film. (We need to do a sound recording for the movie.)
3. Ovo *snimanje* će trajati nekoliko sati. (This recording will last for several hours.)
4. Tokom *snimanja* filma, glumci su bili veoma umorni. (During the filming of the movie, the actors were very tired.)
5. Nisam bio zadovoljan kvalitetom *snimka*. (I was not satisfied with the quality of the recording.)
6. Da bismo mogli da prikažemo film, moramo ga prebaciti sa *snimka* na digitalni format. (To be able to show the movie, we need to transfer it from the recording to a digital format.)
7. Producent je bio veoma srećan kada je video *snimak* filma. (The producer was very happy when he saw the movie recording.)
8. *Snimka* govora predsednika je postala viralna na društvenim mrežama. (The recording of the president's speech has gone viral on social media.)
9. Moja omiljena aktivnost je *snimanje* videozapisa. (My favorite activity is recording videos.)
10. *Snimanje* albuma je trajalo tri meseca. (Recording the album took three months.)

(Note: The word "snimanje" is the noun form of the verb "snimati," which means "to record." In these sentences, it is used in various contexts, such as in the context of recording audio, video, and movies.)